cz.cvut.fel.matyapav.afandroid.components.types

Class AFTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cvut.fel.matyapav.afandroid.components.types.AFComponent
      • cz.cvut.fel.matyapav.afandroid.components.types.AFTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AbstractComponent

    public class AFTable
extends AFComponent
    Represents table component. This component should be used only when there is space for it, that means table can be used on tablets but it is not suitable for mobile phones. This class was not fully debugged and probably won't be fully prepared for using. This component was replaced by AFList, but has been left in project for future needs.
    Since:
    1.0.0.
